  startDialogue:
  - "\"Ta nghe n\xF3i g\u1EA7n \u0111\xE2y ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta \u0111ang \u0111\u1ED3n
    th\u1ED5i v\u1EC1 1 t\u1EA5m b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 kho b\xE1u..! \""
  - "\"Nghe c\xF3 v\u1EBB r\u1EA5t qu\xFD gi\xE1\""
  - "\"N\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng phi\u1EC1n c\u1EADu c\xF3 th\u1EC3 gi\xFAp ta t\xECm ki\u1EBFm
    n\xF3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c kh\xF4ng ?\""
  progressDialogue:
  - "\"C\xF4ng cu\u1ED9c t\xECm ki\u1EBFm \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE2u r\u1ED3i anh
    b\u1EA1n\""
  completeDialogue:
  - "\"Anh b\u1EA1n gi\u1ECFi th\u1EADt, th\xEA c\u0169ng t\xECm ra t\u1EA5m b\u1EA3n
    \u0111\u1ED3 n\xE0y\""
  - "\"T\xF4i t\u1EF1 h\xE0o v\u1EC1 c\u1EADu\""
  - "\"G\u1EEDi c\u1EADu ch\xFAt v\xE0ng l\xE0m l\u1EC7 ph\xED nh\xE1\""
